svg.source: Title: User Keep Track of Invitations User-->Guest: Sends Invite Email through System Guest-->Email: Clicks link on email invite Email-->User Interface: Open accepting page Guest-->User Interface: Clicks accept invite User Interface-->Server API: Calls accept invite API Server API-->Server API: Validates Data Note right of Server API: If error, return with error Server API-->Database: Update guest invite to accepted Database-->Server API: Saved guest invite Server API-->Email Platform: Send thanks for accepting invite and calendar reminder email Server API-->User Interface: Saved guest json User Interface-->User Interface: Show success message User Interface-->Guest: Asks to login or register for account Note right of Guest: Only logged in guests can add gift ideas User-->User Interface:See List of Guests User Interface-->Server API: Calls list guests API Server API-->Database: Get guest list w/ status Database-->Server API: List of guests w/ status Server API-->User Interface: List of guests w/ status User Interface-->User: Display guests with status
